Program: Outlook
Title: I Woke Up During Surgery
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p04p5zt4
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 Jan 2017
Donna Penner was admitted to hospital for surgery. It should have been a straightforward procedure but Donna woke up during the operation and was completely unable to alert the doctors. William Lindesay describes himself as a "wall nut". He's been obsessed with the Great Wall of China since he was a child and he recently drove the full length of it. Laila Haidari is called the "mother" of Kabul's drug addicts. Afghanistan produces 90% of the world's opium and has a huge heroin addiction problem. Laila has devoted her life to helping thousands of those addicts. (Photo: In the operating theatre. Credit: Ulrich Baumgarten/Getty Images) Show less